{"tid":1540490,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"831 Police unacceptable actions at  Prince Edward conclusion","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T07:58:34.000Z","uid":112391,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"767a41aee62000784326234d6abd67354e4129fd","tid":1540490,"uid":112391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:37:41.000Z","msg":"According to the nongovernmental press conference at September 5th, two arrestee report that there are some UNACCEPTABLE actions by police, and those actions seriously violation of human rights.<br />\n<br />\n1. Doubt of killing citizens and.<br />\n<br />\n-A person has been beat by police(Elite Team) for about <span style=\"color: red;\">half hours</span>(observed by video), and <span style=\"color: red;\">foam appear at his mouth</span>. Police is <span style=\"color: red;\">fail to asking for his attention</span> and <span style=\"color: red;\">start to do CPR on him</span>. After about ten minutes, 4 firemen arrive and take him away.<span style=\"color: red;\"> No one knows where he went</span>. (02:30)<br />\n<br />\n-The arrestee claim that all patients <span style=\"color: red;\">should be sent to PMH</span>(Princess Margaret Hospital), but the police conference claim that <span style=\"color: red;\">no one dead</span> at <span style=\"color: red;\">KWH</span>(Kwong Wah Hospital). (05:56)<br />\n<br />\n-The police(elite team) walking downward though electric staircase and <span style=\"color: red;\">citizens' back of body, or even head</span>. Citizens shout 'help' and being <span style=\"color: red;\">yelled by 'shut up'</span>. (10:08)<br />\n<br />\n2. Dehumanization and Violation at their human rights.<br />\n-Police curse the arrestee as<span style=\"color: red;\"> cockroaches and pussy</span>. (03:38)<br />\n<br />\n-Police talk to the arrestee &quot; we worked so hard for this two months(talking about the protests), it is reasonable that <span style=\"color: red;\">we want to fuck</span> those female protester&quot;. (12:50)<br />\n<br />\n-A female arrestee's<span style=\"color: red;\"> breast has been touched</span> by a police(man), at the police station. (04:50)<br />\n<br />\n-The same female arrestee required to<span style=\"color: red;\"> close the door during toileting</span>, but<span style=\"color: red;\"> rejected</span> by two police women with reason &quot;we have the same thing&quot;, and <span style=\"color: red;\">facing to the arrestee</span>. At the same time, police man stay nearby .(Please notes: this is <span style=\"color: red;\">NOT the FIRST CLAIM</span> during the few weeks.) (05:00)<br />\n<br />\n-The<span style=\"color: red;\"> male</span> arrestee also <span style=\"color: red;\">being watched</span> by side when he is<span style=\"color: red;\"> toileting</span>.(16:50)<br />\n<br />\n-A Japanese have been arrested, police said 'Japanese Consulate rest at Sunday' and <span style=\"color: red;\">can do nothing</span>. We don't know how is going on. (13:50)<br />\n<br />\n3. Unreasonable actions.<br />\n<br />\n-Some arrestee had been sent to<span style=\"color: red;\"> SUL</span> (San Uk Lang holding centre), <span style=\"color: red;\">without any reason</span>.(Please noted: At the previous arrest, it found that many arrestee <span style=\"color: red;\">had been seriously injured after they leave SUL</span>. There is <span style=\"color: red;\">no cctv</span> in the interview room and the search room. Some <span style=\"color: red;\">rumor claim that a female had been raped</span> and we still waiting for the truth.)(33:10)<br />\n<br />\n-Some of the <span style=\"color: red;\">arrestee</span> have been <span style=\"color: red;\">high-light and noted 5 stars</span> (example: a social worker who always stand between police and protesters) at the name-list. (34:10)<br />\n<br />\nPlease keep updating HK, since we have <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5 Declaration, not one less.</span></span><br />\nAlthough Carrie Lam said few times the bills was totally dead, or she withdraw the bill today, she still a person that TOTALLY UNTRUSTWORTHY as CCP. That's why we are still fighting on the street. The HKers will keep fighting for what we should fight, for our family, for freedom, and for Hong Kong, until we all dead.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Liberate Hong Kong, the revolution of our times</span></span><br />\n<br />\nThank you for your kind attention.<br />\n<br />\n*Note<br />\n70 people has been arrested in total, some of them are from Hong Kong island. (36:00)"},{"pid":"5d239e6073bc9b90f529c8f05ffdaa87bc361371","tid":1540490,"uid":112391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:37:54.000Z","msg":"Source: (Chinese)<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n唔好意思咁多位巴打, 無意騎劫領功, 但係我開始做果陣(大約1700)未見到有人做, 所以搶住做左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝巴打做左中文版, 方便我打, 如果可能既幫我補充下, 或者推上去比外國睇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">核彈！！831太子站恐襲受害者證言！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538929\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538929</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">［整理］831太子站目擊者證言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539084</a></span><br />\n-有機會有一個人死左 比警察打左半個鐘 嘔白泡 差佬見佢冇反應 之後冇打 二三十分鐘後由消防員 非救護人員 送走 完全冇反應(02:30)<br />\n-目擊者話傷者係送去瑪嘉烈唔係廣華(警記招話冇人係廣華死)(05:56)<br />\n-速龍落電梯 踩住市民背部甚至頭部落(10:08)<br />\n----<br />\n-鬧示威者甲由臭閪(03:38)<br />\n-差佬同佢地講<span style=\"color: red;\">想</span>強姦佢地係正常(12:50)<br />\n-有被捕人士係警署被非禮 (摸胸)(04:50)<br />\n-係警署去廁所時不能關門 而當時有其他性別既警員在場(05:00)<br />\n-有日本人被捕 警方拒絕比佢聯繫大使館(13:50)<br />\n----<br />\n-凌晨時分有部分被拘捕人士送上全黑車往新屋嶺(33:10)<br />\n-被捕人士名單有備注（例如：知名社工）(34:10)<br />\n-去晒葵涌警署有70人（當中有啲係港島拘捕）(36:00)<br />\n</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6f7ff3322043ea8a2decf4c1bf2a8925e4861e74","tid":1540490,"uid":302831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:39:07.000Z","msg":"全面抵制藍色餐廳<br />\n一齊打經濟戰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.289809900000016%2C114.1965917&amp;z=17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs%26shorturl%3D1%26ll%3D22.289809900000016%252C114.1965917%26z%3D17&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbjizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=f2264c4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.289809900000016%2C114.1965917&amp;z=17</a>"},{"pid":"c826cea7aba24a77cbfba8312f668e9790e1c2c0","tid":1540490,"uid":285766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:40:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Five</span></span>"},{"pid":"53433d5649057713bbe13e540b1b7a743aaddac8","tid":1540490,"uid":278431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:40:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8dfc2d8039ae407ffbbe954bb1a8c2f01928a505","tid":1540490,"uid":112391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:42:49.000Z","msg":"5 Declaration<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/drLkeTj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdrLkeTj.jpg&h=a1b45e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nfrom: Winter on fire"},{"pid":"92ef76e1d9b5ef83390fa2c8184a16c7196a658f","tid":1540490,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:43:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"